    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, glass-like shine, and the interior remains in pristine, original condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having received regular preventative maintenance and driven only sparingly. This is a collector-grade example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
