    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-shifted Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical provenance is exceptional: the rod bearing recall has been addressed, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates. The VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, ensuring optimal variable valve timing. The chassis remains taut with original suspension geometry and factory-spec bushings. The exterior retains its factory deep-gloss finish with zero oxidation, while the undercarriage is devoid of corrosion. This is a collector-grade E46, free of common failure points, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
      "price": 44500.0,
